    "Title": "RESOURCE DRIVE: LARGE CARGO NEEDS HAULING",
    "TitleKey": "GoblinG_ArcCorp_HaulCargo_L_Title",
    "Description": "El here.\n\nIf you\u2019re looking to make some creds and have a ship that can take at least <EM4>~mission(MissionMaxSCUSize) cargo containers</EM4>, head over to <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4>. This is a big haul, so it\u2019d be good to bring a <EM4>heavy-duty tractor beam</EM4>, and maybe even a <EM4>couple extra hands</EM4> to help you out.\n\nOnce you\u2019ve got the resources from the freight elevator, take them to a freight elevator at: <EM4>~mission(Destination|Address|ListAll)</EM4>. I\u2019ve got someone on hand to process them for you and then we can sort your payment out.\n\nEvery bit helps ArcCorp get closer to securing a win.\n\n\nElla Tieno\nContractor Liaison Officer\nArcCorp",
    "DescriptionKey": "GoblinG_ArcCorp_HaulCargo_L_Desc",
    "DisplayDescription": "El here.\n\nIf you\u2019re looking to make some creds and have a ship that can take at least <EM4>4 SCU cargo containers</EM4>, head over to <EM4>ArcCorp Mining Area 045</EM4>. This is a big haul, so it\u2019d be good to bring a <EM4>heavy-duty tractor beam</EM4>, and maybe even a <EM4>couple extra hands</EM4> to help you out.\n\nOnce you\u2019ve got the resources from the freight elevator, take them to a freight elevator at: <EM4>Area18</EM4>. I\u2019ve got someone on hand to process them for you and then we can sort your payment out.\n\nEvery bit helps ArcCorp get closer to securing a win.\n\n\nElla Tieno\nContractor Liaison Officer\nArcCorp",
